{"ts":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-4e12"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Public SDK transaction boundary: atomic multi-item + relationship-event commit primitive"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"The pm-vcs exemplar (PR#587) exposed the one waived SDK gap in packages/pm-vcs/GAP_REPORT.md: there is no public transaction boundary committing a multi-item mutation together with relationship events. The exemplar compensates with a bespoke crash-consistency protocol (event-first write order, deterministic merge event identity, idempotent duplicate-append recovery, fail-closed conflicts) that every foreign-domain package would otherwise have to reinvent. Ship a first-class SDK commit primitive: all-or-nothing observable state across item store + relationship event stream, crash-safe at every partial-write point, preserving immutable-history append-only semantics (no rollback rewrites — compensation/reconciliation on replay). Migrate pm-vcs merge onto it as the acceptance vehicle, or record precisely why the bespoke protocol must remain."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["concurrency","extensibility","sdk","universal-tool"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":480},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Public SDK primitive commits multi-item mutations + relationship events with all-or-nothing observable state; failure-injection coverage for every partial-write direction and crash point; pm-vcs merge migrated onto the primitive (or a recorded justified waiver); contract docs + SDK.md published; no history-stream rewrite semantics introduced"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-usfg"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-8ngt","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"},{"id":"pm-dj98","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"},{"id":"pm-ju83","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"},{"id":"pm-klo8","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:03:42.541Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"58495d893acc3ba47867b2c4362c36b73d3a9c88485c42ffe4368dd2ed30a150","message":""}
