{"ts":"2026-07-18T16:49:47.732Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/4","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-18T16:49:47.732Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Hosted PR #605 review round 1 evidence: accepted eight valid recovery/compensation findings and declined one pm-docs false positive with live metadata proof. Hardened runtime input types, journal lifecycle invariants, null-prototype result maps, inspection-authoritative recovery, VCS original-ref restoration, transaction-owned compensation, retry event identity, and item+relationship post-commit validation. All nine inline threads were reacted to, answered contextually, and resolved; Gemini, Greptile, CodeRabbit, Codecov, CodSpeed, and Sourcery artifacts were individually reacted to and acknowledged. Verification: linked pm tests passed; 311 files / 5,916 tests at exact 100/100/100/100 (39,078 statements, 27,482 branches, 7,957 functions, 38,043 lines); lint, zero clones, static complexity, 100% docstrings, package boundary, token budget, secrets, audit, and packed VCS+SDK replay at /tmp/pm-sdk-transaction-review-proof-bM6GcR all pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T16:49:47.732Z"}],"before_hash":"249d695210ff9d3db81407618f725b9c071e37132277d5b89ba61e39834bcb9e","after_hash":"eb00455e362c34eb024032ec813cad8873400ef30026f1e838c11634e19bf0e3"}
{"ts":"2026-07-18T16:49:48.444Z","author":"codex-root","op":"learning_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T16:49:48.444Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/learnings","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-18T16:49:48.441Z","author":"codex-root","text":"A transaction journal is a recovery hint, never stronger than current domain inspection: validate lifecycle invariants at load, rebuild completion from inspections, and make every compensation conditional on still owning the exact state it intends to reverse."}]}],"before_hash":"eb00455e362c34eb024032ec813cad8873400ef30026f1e838c11634e19bf0e3","after_hash":"cca23e5b9e14d2c023f291e0bcbfe3e80412a3d303e3f6c6f9c991ead6b26d71"}
