{"ts":"2026-07-18T17:21:26.778Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/6","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-18T17:21:26.774Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Pre-push Greptile 83e0a668 P1 resolved: compensation now writes durable compensating state before any domain inspection, reconciles all steps in reverse order, and invokes each step's idempotent transaction-owned compensation when inspection itself fails. A regression reproduces an inspection conflict after an earlier step applied, verifies the journal reaches compensated without manual deletion, clears the conflict, and proves the next attempt commits. Verification: focused 14 tests pass, strict static/docstring/package/token gates pass, and full repository coverage passes 311 files / 5,917 tests at exact 100/100/100/100 (39,077 statements, 27,480 branches, 7,957 functions, 38,043 lines)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T17:21:26.778Z"}],"before_hash":"cfd6f5888688574fc69e48c4cadb971cd8a9e70f226db8fb5b4d7dc45a3fe557","after_hash":"c71e8f8589d9bda003b2e31f4252cfdb6aab12a7dc7d800c183ff6b1aad6f057"}
